{"tid":190984,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"老母想做生意 好撚苦惱","createTime":"2017-04-07T13:22:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-12T12:03:25.000Z","uid":32932,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4b8c49d424874536ac3a72ede82699490e5caf5e","tid":190984,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:22:05.000Z","msg":"想問下長發街市有咩好食<br />\n燒烤、糖水質素如何？？<br />\n<br />\n你地覺得美食城有咩野食可以賣？？<br />\n<br />\n我老母成日想開間鋪頭仔賣野食<br />\n佢而家諗緊頂人手開鋪頭<br />\n好驚間鋪有咩問題搵傻仔接手<br />\n<br />\n我：你覺得自己有咩優勝地方令人地幫襯你<br />\n佢：因為我整得好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我：你想整既野 你試過整未 <br />\n佢：未 <br />\n我：咁你自信邊到黎 <br />\n佢：其實唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我：咁易做到點解人地整得咁難食 <br />\n佢：我會肯花心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n問佢入貨貨源、鋪頭目標顧客etc 全部都答唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢去算命算到自己做生意會唔好<br />\n要用我名義去開呢間鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要我放假去幫手<br />\n<br />\n但我今年畢業 唔知會做邊行 唔知得唔得閒幫佢手<br />\n佢話我讀濕鳩文科 畢業出黎都冇野做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢今個月或者下個月就要接手 <br />\n我今個月又要FYP又勁多功課，下個月考試 考完試就要去外國做個幾月義工 <br />\n換言之我係完全冇時間幫佢<br />\n但佢話識人個女幫佢上網搵貨源<br />\n又想我幫佢設計宣傳野<br />\n<br />\n好苦惱 佢投資一向都冇眼光<br />\n十幾萬倒錢落海 屌 我同佢講 我寧願佢拎十幾萬去買六合彩 都好過白做一場仲要蝕晒d錢"},{"pid":"56283814297f63f204273b409ad00cc2217e7471","tid":190984,"uid":51889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:24:04.000Z","msg":"19"},{"pid":"216f403629e5489f6ff903e3bb728d77049b3ca4","tid":190984,"uid":33190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:27:25.000Z","msg":"企硬<br />\n跟佢衰硬"},{"pid":"4105d39c15c8a548d35d725ea23d16ade3bdfa21","tid":190984,"uid":98041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:31:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同樣苦惱<br />\n好彩老母最近提少左呢件事"},{"pid":"944897e590e5dfbc584ff1ce624afeaed23a70da","tid":190984,"uid":11914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:32:14.000Z","msg":"一定出事<br />\n十個開鋪 搞得掂嘅可能一個都冇"},{"pid":"af304a2f23e7dc829dcf40dd9593899d854d4ff6","tid":190984,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:43:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>19</blockquote><br />\n咩19"},{"pid":"e7ce235948286caf79077932358d2b7ccc99afd0","tid":190984,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:43:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同樣苦惱<br />\n好彩老母最近提少左呢件事</blockquote><br />\n你係咪我家姐"},{"pid":"ac0f87b62799d6be20c0458e68b52abf780f1783","tid":190984,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:44:05.000Z","msg":"屌我呀媽一返工就好盡心盡力<br />\n所以成日想自己開鋪"},{"pid":"40e920fd0f3668e6673a632daceed00a1babaadf","tid":190984,"uid":68568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:48:56.000Z","msg":"家底點？如果ok嘅話比幾十萬搏下都好，最緊要身體唔好去咁盡"},{"pid":"293d3d19b326b498c813523f2dec9b6db16a5684","tid":190984,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:49:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同樣苦惱<br />\n好彩老母最近提少左呢件事</blockquote><br />\n你係咪我家姐</blockquote><br />\n我家姐叫我呀媽去試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲借錢畀佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7385e6b529b452fd4abd383b92b46f6378354868","tid":190984,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:50:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>家底點？如果ok嘅話比幾十萬搏下都好，最緊要身體唔好去咁盡</blockquote><br />\n唔係好清楚 但遲d全家去旅行 佢又話要節衣縮食"},{"pid":"cd104fbe069ef8ebce243fadd481db49afd6a3f8","tid":190984,"uid":98041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T16:04:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同樣苦惱<br />\n好彩老母最近提少左呢件事</blockquote><br />\n你係咪我家姐</blockquote><br />\n我家姐叫我呀媽去試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲借錢畀佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我無細佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"677696933553f292c9ddbfb090cb9874e4ee92a7","tid":190984,"uid":44559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T16:09:35.000Z","msg":"叫佢係果到搵份工做下，做熟左先<br />\n<br />\n計下人地搵唔搵到，再做囉"},{"pid":"665d89a76350e48e547260351ff2953b3b3e30c9","tid":190984,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T17:45:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫佢係果到搵份工做下，做熟左先<br />\n<br />\n計下人地搵唔搵到，再做囉</blockquote><br />\n有講過"},{"pid":"d7f7dbf44a4396df95a550766b381296ed54a9e0","tid":190984,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T17:45:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同樣苦惱<br />\n好彩老母最近提少左呢件事</blockquote><br />\n你係咪我家姐</blockquote><br />\n我家姐叫我呀媽去試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲借錢畀佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我無細佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我唔係細佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30a2eecc2ed41c7f769c1c081499ff6fcd74d22a","tid":190984,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T17:52:32.000Z","msg":"好難做,識人係街市做飲食<br />\n租已經玩死<br />\n如果搵到食,小心人地又開多間頂死你<br />\n好多街市熟食,菜檔,肉檔,背後係同一個老闆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccd5f680d8c32cee1a86f1b22f2a26fe83d88ee2","tid":190984,"uid":92063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T18:06:21.000Z","msg":"你阿媽啲思想咁後生既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲妹妹仔成日話來開糖水鋪<br />\n我：識煮？好食？<br />\n妹妹仔：唔識呀。到時再學囉<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71efbbc735caf2c34829cb505c47d63e3394cb0f","tid":190984,"uid":99642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T18:10:19.000Z","msg":"開舖當打工囉<br />\n<br />\n無話唔好 ,錢都係要用來用既<br />\n<br />\n伯母開心咪得<br />\n<br />\n做生意係有有時係有賺蝕架啦"},{"pid":"cb37fd646d8f046d6c8ac8ef2f83c5dfde723578","tid":190984,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T18:12:17.000Z","msg":"你去間鋪食下野睇下環境點先"},{"pid":"392419eb21b4ca0599454fc7e2b928d0a70dabb3","tid":190984,"uid":53780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T18:47:04.000Z","msg":"下次去你屋企<br />\n叫伯母整d佢將來鋪頭會賣既野我地食<br />\n我地話佢聽好冇食"},{"pid":"9a2f74e9acfda5a1407e28ff38f124d89999c846","tid":190984,"uid":36849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T19:01:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"69d6d86a027ad2d76d8526a762bdad2670a0cd96","tid":190984,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T03:11:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好做建華場 死硬 <br />\n唔好講交唔交到租 貨款你返唔返到都係問題<br />\n同埋上網睇頂手果d 咩唔洗落手做 利潤幾多 呃鳩你<br />\n我老友叫人放上去頂手 蝕緊5-6萬 利潤打靜賺5萬<br />\n<br />\n信唔信就你諗<br />\n<br />\n如果你老母真係想做下事頭婆 就搵間細鋪做<br />\n唔好同人頂，有錢賺會頂比你？<br />\n咩店主移民阿 要照顧仔女阿 果d是撚但打上去</blockquote><br />\n點解唔好做建華場<br />\n長發就係建華啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"836112028bfec4d560f939a89b3b06b4675870cf","tid":190984,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T03:12:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔好做建華場 死硬 <br />\n唔好講交唔交到租 貨款你返唔返到都係問題<br />\n同埋上網睇頂手果d 咩唔洗落手做 利潤幾多 呃鳩你<br />\n我老友叫人放上去頂手 蝕緊5-6萬 利潤打靜賺5萬<br />\n<br />\n信唔信就你諗<br />\n<br />\n如果你老母真係想做下事頭婆 就搵間細鋪做<br />\n唔好同人頂，有錢賺會頂比你？<br />\n咩店主移民阿 要照顧仔女阿 果d是撚但打上去</blockquote><br />\n點解唔好做建華場<br />\n長發就係建華啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢話間鋪個老細有幾間分店 係另一個場有間好好生意 全家都去幫手 長發呢間就完全冇理 所以先搵人頂"},{"pid":"ae4f7526fa4ab1df350c6b4ee1a3250384637435","tid":190984,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T03:13:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開舖當打工囉<br />\n<br />\n無話唔好 ,錢都係要用來用既<br />\n<br />\n伯母開心咪得<br />\n<br />\n做生意係有有時係有賺蝕架啦</blockquote><br />\n我寧願佢拎筆錢去下旅行 好過做到隻積咁仲要蝕晒d錢"},{"pid":"32e9189d8520b3a200ffd51e1e860224af331898","tid":190984,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T03:13:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好做建華場 死硬 <br />\n唔好講交唔交到租 貨款你返唔返到都係問題<br />\n同埋上網睇頂手果d 咩唔洗落手做 利潤幾多 呃鳩你<br />\n我老友叫人放上去頂手 蝕緊5-6萬 利潤打靜賺5萬<br />\n<br />\n信唔信就你諗<br />\n<br />\n如果你老母真係想做下事頭婆 就搵間細鋪做<br />\n唔好同人頂，有錢賺會頂比你？<br />\n咩店主移民阿 要照顧仔女阿 果d是撚但打上去</blockquote><br />\n我梗係唔信佢有得賺會畀人做啦<br />\n但我老母好自信覺得佢會做得好"},{"pid":"6333d67cbcb73f9490e2c6a3b14fd2262ade85a8","tid":190984,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T03:14:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你阿媽啲思想咁後生既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲妹妹仔成日話來開糖水鋪<br />\n我：識煮？好食？<br />\n妹妹仔：唔識呀。到時再學囉<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n腦筍都未生埋既mk妹咁 屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe85dfcc43db43cce409c7b6aa5aa83197809fb7","tid":190984,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T03:15:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好難做,識人係街市做飲食<br />\n租已經玩死<br />\n如果搵到食,小心人地又開多間頂死你<br />\n好多街市熟食,菜檔,肉檔,背後係同一個老闆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢話預左頭一個月會蝕"},{"pid":"b690a6007aab60c5fe96e4d3b961bf9b02d9b672","tid":190984,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T03:15:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下次去你屋企<br />\n叫伯母整d佢將來鋪頭會賣既野我地食<br />\n我地話佢聽好冇食</blockquote><br />\n你黎幫手啦"},{"pid":"de2acb55bfeb151848df6a7ae2da7cd65f04d1cb","tid":190984,"uid":83825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T03:18:13.000Z","msg":"同我呀媽一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蝕緊幾十萬 <br />\n阻止下佢啦 到時都係搞到自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3de98071288a9723859db65be5e088e9abac1599","tid":190984,"uid":86275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T03:21:42.000Z","msg":"我老母之前都問過我<br />\n旦係都一一比我拒絕<br />\n佢就死死氣唔去開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b284af4a8880b6950bd12dbe403883b2dd8540","tid":190984,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T03:28:34.000Z","msg":"博一博 單車變摩托"},{"pid":"0f9d384f1f08bc34d3dae61ad3b9ef8d7bdb736d","tid":190984,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T03:35:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>博一博 單車變摩托</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"801594d91c7542a9f0cabf6e6a4d900f4a817ea2","tid":190984,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T03:36:20.000Z","msg":"上一手開左幾個月 蝕左三十萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3d795a4df7d6f57d12b98cb673a320050ebba8e","tid":190984,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T03:36:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同我呀媽一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蝕緊幾十萬 <br />\n阻止下佢啦 到時都係搞到自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪你係業主"},{"pid":"35fffcd5aa1164a912792bbed23366c98825e413","tid":190984,"uid":59641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T03:39:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>下次去你屋企<br />\n叫伯母整d佢將來鋪頭會賣既野我地食<br />\n我地話佢聽好冇食</blockquote><br />\n你黎幫手啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nagger, 可以的話我都幫手試食"},{"pid":"50570531e60f9088db877f6159fcc6a2a4ff8147","tid":190984,"uid":14605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T03:43:55.000Z","msg":"過來人，唔好比老母做生意，比佢搞到屋企慘左10幾年"},{"pid":"acd5832c698a2d2e8c3ce749f5eb44a77655baa1","tid":190984,"uid":83825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T03:44:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同我呀媽一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蝕緊幾十萬 <br />\n阻止下佢啦 到時都係搞到自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪你係業主</blockquote><br />\n我老母直接挑戰鋪頭呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我當初又係問佢你問果啲問題<br />\n佢又係類似你媽媽咁答<br />\n根本呢啲人就冇生意頭腦又唔肯聽人講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢約都簽埋先同我講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所有時間除左翻學/翻工 佢都覺得你要係鋪頭<br />\n同朋友食個飯行個街都會比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主要盡力阻 不歸路黎"},{"pid":"4b5eef51a8af3b52a19defe7ec5d6ceea419c0cf","tid":190984,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T04:05:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同我呀媽一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蝕緊幾十萬 <br />\n阻止下佢啦 到時都係搞到自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪你係業主</blockquote><br />\n我老母直接挑戰鋪頭呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我當初又係問佢你問果啲問題<br />\n佢又係類似你媽媽咁答<br />\n根本呢啲人就冇生意頭腦又唔肯聽人講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢約都簽埋先同我講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所有時間除左翻學/翻工 佢都覺得你要係鋪頭<br />\n同朋友食個飯行個街都會比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主要盡力阻 不歸路黎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢話我同家姐因為十萬幾係到嘈嘈閉 <br />\n佢自己都拎唔到出黎 屌"},{"pid":"a7053f6e14e19f025b506ccf194d5f813f41450c","tid":190984,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T04:05:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>下次去你屋企<br />\n叫伯母整d佢將來鋪頭會賣既野我地食<br />\n我地話佢聽好冇食</blockquote><br />\n你黎幫手啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nagger, 可以的話我都幫手試食</blockquote><br />\n咁客氣呀"},{"pid":"1a18202c5e396020456bde4c3052c74cdac2e9ac","tid":190984,"uid":83825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T04:16:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同我呀媽一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蝕緊幾十萬 <br />\n阻止下佢啦 到時都係搞到自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪你係業主</blockquote><br />\n我老母直接挑戰鋪頭呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我當初又係問佢你問果啲問題<br />\n佢又係類似你媽媽咁答<br />\n根本呢啲人就冇生意頭腦又唔肯聽人講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢約都簽埋先同我講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所有時間除左翻學/翻工 佢都覺得你要係鋪頭<br />\n同朋友食個飯行個街都會比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主要盡力阻 不歸路黎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢話我同家姐因為十萬幾係到嘈嘈閉 <br />\n佢自己都拎唔到出黎 屌</blockquote><br />\n佢果陣叫我申請大專既生活貸款比佢用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80d0223cd5bed68621fa776b04c388fe9ce7c2a4","tid":190984,"uid":8216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T04:17:23.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過佢其實係睇死你畢業無人請 所以依家起定個落台階比你先？"},{"pid":"5e7aa332bafe28aaf38ba491f83ac3092bae26f7","tid":190984,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T04:41:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇諗過佢其實係睇死你畢業無人請 所以依家起定個落台階比你先？</blockquote><br />\n佢應該諗住我放假就去幫手"},{"pid":"f3a17b9984ecad327aa1607aa186ecb740e08ad1","tid":190984,"uid":27368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T04:49:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇諗過佢其實係睇死你畢業無人請 所以依家起定個落台階比你先？</blockquote><br />\n佢應該諗住我放假就去幫手</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同佢講要俾人工<br />\n一門生意要靠有人幫先得賺其實係fail<br />\n你放假係有薪假 所以佢俾人工係應份<br />\n<br />\n利申 由細兩老開檔 日日做到狗都蝕 <br />\n後尾幫佢地重整成盤生意先有返錢賺<br />\n以後佢地覺得後生要幫手 宜家佢地明左生意要自己做都有錢賺 而唔係靠人地幫"},{"pid":"53ea56e0c508b909f8c9e0ef7503c560da05273d","tid":190984,"uid":27368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T04:50:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇諗過佢其實係睇死你畢業無人請 所以依家起定個落台階比你先？</blockquote><br />\n佢應該諗住我放假就去幫手</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同佢講要俾人工<br />\n一門生意要靠有人幫先得賺其實係fail<br />\n你放假係有薪假 所以佢俾人工係應份<br />\n<br />\n利申 由細兩老開檔 日日做到狗都蝕 <br />\n後尾幫佢地重整成盤生意先有返錢賺<br />\n以<span style=\"color: red;\">前</span>佢地覺得後生要幫手 宜家佢地明左生意要自己做都有錢賺 而唔